{"tid":2161228,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"8.3清場案 寫錯被告身高 警長晉升試狀元稱不懂如何更正供詞","createTime":"2020-08-17T12:25:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T12:55:59.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b0527b26571308dcf56bf1546c4d999bb1cc50c9","tid":2161228,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T12:25:29.000Z","msg":"（獨媒特約報導）去年8月3日的「旺角再遊行」，入夜後有大批示威者於旺角區設置路障堵路，9人被控非法集結罪，今日（17日）在九龍城裁判法院續審。負責制服其中一名被告的「速龍」為十多年前警長晉升試的狀元，接受《警聲》訪問時稱熟讀《警察通例》，惟他庭上被揭在此案及另一案的供詞均出現錯處，更曾表示不知道從什麼途徑糾正口供。被問及記錄被告的特徵包括身高是否重要時，警長僅回應「不予置評」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1076533\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1076533&d=hvnZYtOEdtVTkBm9e3s21A0QAWntaMGUWBfwPSaCbl8%3D&h=d850c2f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1076533&h=881b5890\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1076533</a>"},{"pid":"a914fec7e90013981213e3029ba7124265bc3a34","tid":2161228,"uid":132587,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T12:28:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b5b753388fddd1402ff7f692a566ce7927265a98","tid":2161228,"uid":259901,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T12:33:58.000Z","msg":"狗入面最聰明嗰隻狗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲係狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n即係綠毛蟲再勁都進化唔到做烈空坐架，天生架呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"299527b2677c331a9c4ddf15ffc841020b9daac4","tid":2161228,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T12:35:03.000Z","msg":"做左十年都仲係三柴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e3e71001901647c118673332295802117b6becc","tid":2161228,"uid":255637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime